One concept I'd love to see (although I suspect it's already been done but obviously it's impossible to check every single factbook ever) is a nation that's one of those horrible totalitarian nations but they present all their factbooks as in-character propaganda that denies all the bad shit they do.

Cause I tend to notice that even 'evil' nations will write their factbooks very matter-of-factly, for lack of a better term. But I'd love one that tries to pretend that it's actually a super-good and caring nation that all its citizens love with the information it presents to outsiders. Maybe as a bonus make it economically-weak like North Korea but its propaganda acting likes its a super prosperous nation.

(And then they'd have a factbook written from the POV of an observer from outside the state talking about how shit really is in their little hellscape)
